Rob McElhenney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rob_McElhenney 0 Robert McElhenney (born April 14, 1977) is an actor, director, producer, and screenwriter. He is known for playing Mac on the FX/FXX comedy series It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia. He is also one of the developers, executive producers, and the creator of the show, which has provided him with writing and directing credits on various episodes.
